sequenceDiagram
    participant Editor as Claude Code
    participant LSP as LSP服务器(TypeScript LS)
    
    Editor->>LSP: initialize (capabilities)
    LSP-->>Editor: initialized + serverCapabilities
    
    Editor->>LSP: textDocument/didOpen (uri, content)
    LSP->>LSP: 索引文件（异步，1-3s）
    
    Editor->>LSP: textDocument/hover (uri, position)
    LSP-->>Editor: Hover (类型信息, docs)
    
    Editor->>LSP: textDocument/definition (uri, position)
    LSP-->>Editor: Location[] (定义位置)
    
    Editor->>LSP: textDocument/publishDiagnostics
    LSP-->>Editor: Diagnostic[] (错误 & 警告)
